metadata.name: Polyfier
metadata.description: This is Pimoggy's Polyfier- A pacifier made from Polyethylene, the most common and delicious single use plastic type produced by humans. With out it's Polyfier, Pimoggy is thrown into a hysterical fit due to plastic withdrawal. Pimoggy's are LITERALLY addicted to plastic, and need a constant supply of it. the Polyfier helps satiate their plastic craving until they are given plastic to eat.
